title: Liberty Under Threat
author: citylion
pages:
#- Context:

§0Our ideological neighbors in Anvard are under attack, and their capital city remains occupied. Mayor ComradeNick has now asked all Augustan citizens to aid him in the drilling of vault holes and trenches.§r
#- Written by Citylion on 5/2/2020

§0Throughout the past eight years, Mount Augusta has been a guiding force for democracy, liberty, and justice within Civ. What has made Mount Augusta last, , and what has made Mount Augusta special,§r
#- is not our military power, nor our economic influence, but the sheer willpower of our citizens. Mount Augusta is, and has always been, the place for strong-willed players who want to be free. But Mount Augusta has not always been free.
#- But Mount Augusta has not always been free. Throughout our history, our liberty has been attacked. And in these times, Augustans have come together to defeat their common enemy, whoever it may be. During the HCF invasion on CivCraft 1.0 Mount Auugsta
#- was in ruins. “Nearly every building was demolished, on fire, or covered in lava and cobble spikes.” Most of the other cities that faced this level of griefing were lost to dust, but Mount Augusta refused to give up. In this time of great need 
#- Augustan citizens came together, helped one another, and rebuilt. Once again Mount Augusta is facing a time of great uncertainty, and great need. Our ideological neighbors who strongly value transparency and liberty, are under attack.
#- Every day those who wish to see Mount Augusta crumble defame us, and grow stronger. Now is the time for us to come together and prepare.

§0We know that preparation will deter aggression. We must take action now at this critical and early stage§r
#- in order to protect our freedom.

§0God bless you, and thank you very much.§r
